result.title: Nike Blazer Mid 77 Vintage
result.body: The Nike Blazer Mid 77 Vintage harnesses the old-school look of Nike basketball with a vintage midsole finish, making it look like youve been saving them for years.

result.title: Nike Air Force 1 Shadow
result.body: The Nike Air Force 1 Shadow puts a playful twist on a classic b-ball design. Using a layered approach, doubling the branding and exaggerating the midsole, it highlights AF1 DNA with a bold, feminine look. The rich colors and textures inspired by Coney Island fun let every step pulse with energy.
